		Libtga release 0.1.6		Feb 11 2001


These are the release notes for the Libtga package. The TGA library is a
library to support the TGA image file format. It will be fully compatible 
to the TGA File Format Specification Version 2.0 (see ftp.truevision.com). 


COPYING:

  The Libtga is released under GNU Lesser General Public License.
  All other software (example programs and docs) in this package is released 
  under the GNU General Public License. For more information on the licenses 
  see the the file COPYING in the project's root directory and the corresponding  sub directories.


INSTALLING:

  Instructions on how to install the package the sources can be found in the 
  file INSTALL.


REPORTING BUGS:

  If you want to report a bug or have any problems with this package or want to
  see a feature in a future release either mail the maintainer or post in one
  of the message forums at http://www.sourceforge.net/projects/tgalib


SITES:
  - Download
	http://www.sourceforge.net/projects/tgalib
  - Homepage
	http://tgalib.sourceforge.net
  - anonymous CVS
  	export CVSROOT=:pserver:anonymous@cvs.tgalib.sf.net:/cvsroot/tgalib
  	cvs login
	cvs -z3 co libtga
	
